title: I See You
overview: Pairin works as a nurse in the hospital and has the ability to communicate with the dead. She strives to keep this a secret so that she can pretend to be normal like everyone else. But in reality everyone seems to know about this and tries to avoid her. Only a nurse named New understands her and always accompanies her. Pairin not only has to look after her daily tasks in the hospital but also stop the playful spirit Chaba.
